<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <%- include partial/common_head.ejs %>
    <%- include partial/ga_pre.ejs %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include partial/ga.ejs %>
    <%- include partial/fb.ejs %>

    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="header">
        <a class="logo" href="">
          <img src="images/logo-01@3x.png" alt="muggle.news" class="wb">
        </a>
        <div class="login-box">
          <% if (me) { %>
          <div class="log-on">
            <a href="" class="log-in">
              <img src="<%= me.picture && me.picture.data && me.picture.data.url %>" alt="">
              <span><%= me.name %></span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <% } else { %>
          <a href="/users/login/facebook" class="log-in">
            <img src="images/ico-facebook-01@3x.png" alt="">
            <span>로그인</span>
          </a>
          <% } %>
        </div><!-- e//login -->
      </div><!-- e//header -->

      <div class="container main">
        <div class="contents">
          <h1>머글뉴스</h1>
          <h2>어렵고 복잡한 뉴스를,
            <br>시간에 따라, 처음부터 끝까지
          </h2>
          <p class="img">
            <img src="images/main-visual02.png" alt="">
          </p>
          <p class="desc">
            뉴스레터를 등록하시면 머글뉴스 오픈 소식과 함께 #최순실게이트, #4대강 등 <br>최근 이슈를 시간순으로 정리한 뉴스를 보내드립니다.
          </p>
          <div class="sign-up-email">
            <div class="input-box">
              <input id="email" type="text" placeholder="이메일 주소를 입력하세요.">
            </div>
            <a id="send_pre_user" class="btn-sign-up">등록하기</a>
          </div>
        </div><!-- e//contents -->
      </div><!-- e//container -->

      <div class="who-are">
        <h3>우리가 누구?</h3>
        <div class="muggle-member">
          <ul>
            <li class="no1">
              <div>
                <p class="name">장팸 (jaipam)</p>
                <p class="txt">'흔한 안흔한 기획자''</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="no2">
              <div>
                <p class="name">지디 (GD)</p>
                <p class="txt">'성장하는 개발자'</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="no3">
              <div>
                <p class="name">리엘 (lee_el)</p>
                <p class="txt">'배고픈 콘텐츠 마케터'</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="no4">
              <div>
                <p class="name">BG (Bernard)</p>
                <p class="txt">'스케치하는 디자이너'</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="no5">
              <div>
                <p class="name">바카 (baka)</p>
                <p class="txt">'내멋대로 디자이너'</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="no6">
              <div>
                <p class="name">앨리스 (alice)</p>
                <p class="txt">'공놀이하는 퍼블리셔'</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div><!-- e// who-are-->
    </div><!-- e//wrap -->

    <%- include partial/footer.ejs %>

    <script type="text/javascript" src="/main.bundle.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
  </body>
</html>
